  "text": "Plasmids. The modified pGEX plasmid with an engineered multi-cloning site at the N-terminus of the GST coding sequence was described previously [CITATION_1] . The cDNA of histones H2A, H3, and H4 was amplified by PCR from reverse transcribed total RNA and inserted in frame with GST using restriction endonucleases and T4 DNA ligase (NEB).",
